<div style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; color: #444; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 600px; margin: auto;">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/69/Airbnb_Logo_B%C3%A9lo.svg" alt="Your Logo" style="max-width: 100px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
    <h2 style="color: #333;">Welcome to Our Platform!</h2>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555;">Hello <strong style="color: #333;"><%= @email %></strong>,</p>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555;">Thank you for signing up! Please confirm your email address by clicking the button below:</p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="http://localhost:5173/confirm_account?token=<%= @token %>"
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #fff; background-color: #28a745; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
      Confirm My Account
    </a>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666;">
    If you didn’t sign up for this account, no action is required. You can safely ignore this email.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">
    Alternatively, if you’re unable to click the button, copy and paste the following URL into your browser:
    <br>
    <a href="http://localhost:5173/confirm_account?token=<%= @token %>" style="color: #28a745;">http://localhost:5173/confirm_account?token=<%= @token %></a>
  </p>

  <div style="border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
    <p>Welcome aboard,</p>
    <p>MaNo ❤</p>
  </div>
</div>